Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model

Class Game

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.Game
public class Game extends Object
This class represents the core game model, managing the game state, decks, players, and overall game logic. It interacts with other components to receive player actions and update the game state accordingly.
